27347.text: [27347] StaticText "This module automatically downloads your Google Mail, Contacts & Calendar to separate files. It'll sync only new Mails, Contacts & Events."

27348.text: [27348] StaticText 'This tool will output the following directory structure:'

27349.text:
[27349] StaticText '.
├── Contacts
│   └── *.vcf
├── Calendar
│   └── *.ics
└── Mail
    ├── By ID
    │   └── *.eml
    ├── By Thread
    │   └── <...>
    │       └── *.eml
    └── By Label
        ├── <...>
        │   └── *.eml
        └── [Gmail]
            ├── All Mail
            │   └── *.eml
            ├── Sent
            │   └── *.eml
            └── <...>
                 └── *.eml
'

27350.text: [27350] StaticText "Note: All e-mail files are symlinked to 'By ID/*.eml'."

27352.text: [27352] StaticText 'Google makes great services, but there are many horror stories of people locked out of their accounts. So be safe, and keep your data backed up!'
